{"id":231869166,"title":"摩斯為什麼沒有紙吸管？","content":"很久沒有買摩斯，早上去才發現他給的不是紙吸管，材質是PLA。查了一下PLA才知道，雖然是生物可分解的塑膠，但PLA只能特定環境下分解，分解過程釋放出的溫室氣體是甲烷，是溫室效應最主要的氣體，其效力比二氧化碳頑強21倍。\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/stkPBGD.jpg\n\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N0QC6KvvAXo\nhttps://news.tvbs.com.tw/life/998682\nhttps://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5092141\n\n但其他速食業者或星巴克，其實都在杯口調整，也有提供紙吸管了，這些替代方案雖然稍微改變大家使用習慣，可是也算是方便的。多少能減少一點塑膠材料，對環境更友善一些。\n\n我雖然是不懂為什麼摩斯還是用PLA吸管，也不知道有什麼方式可以影響摩斯（環境議題關注度本來就不高，也很多人覺得方便就好、不要影響我）。目前想到的就是到摩斯網站回饋，希望他們回應客戶建議。\n\n如果你也在意，希望你也可以一起\nhttp://www.mos.com.tw/contact/contactUs.aspx","excerpt":"很久沒有買摩斯，早上去才發現他給的不是紙吸管，材質是PLA。查了一下PLA才知道，雖然是生物可分解的塑膠，但PLA只能特定環境下分解，分解過程釋放出的溫室氣體是甲烷，是溫室效應最主要的氣體，其效力比二","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-08-16T00:35:48.209Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-16T00:36:14.925Z","commentCount":45,"likeCount":54,"tags":[],"topics":["愛地球","環保","減塑","回收","環境"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"國立臺灣大學","department":"地理環境資源學研究所","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":54}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/stkPBGD.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"3ef789c3-ec0c-43d4-a61a-3293bbc3fb96","url":"https://i.imgur.com/stkPBGDl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/stkPBGDl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/stkPBGDl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-16T00:35:48.209Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-16T00:36:14.925Z"},{"id":"3ef789c3-ec0c-43d4-a61a-3293bbc3fb96","url":"http://i.imgur.com/stkPBGD.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/stkPBGD","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/stkPBGDl.jp